* Welcome page, information and links to public pages
* Admin
Admin page which can add classes and skills
It can add a skill based on TL3 version, frontend will always use the latest when creating a new build, but older builds will then still show the version it was saved with
* Accounts
Accounts to save builds on
* Skill calculator for all classes and relics
* Leveling feature
Show exactly what to put a point in at what level
* Save feature
Save builds to your account with name, description
Can be public or private
* Shareable links
* Voting
Public page with weekly voted builds, monthly voted builds and yearly voted builds.
Also browse builds that are public.